Package org.swisscheese.swisscheese.engine.imageEffects

Package for classes and objects relating to effects that can be done on images/color values.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChangeGamma
    Gamma changing effect.
    ImageEffect
    An abstract class for image effects.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GammaState
    A state enum to track if the image that is being affected by ChangeGamma will need to be darkened, brightened, or to remain normal.
